data.value:
This wizard will assist you in the creation and upload process of a DotNetNuke Community instance on Windows Azure Platform.
On the next steps, you must specify the configuration parameters for the instances, so you should be familiar with the DNN Azure deployment architecture. If you have any doubt, please visit http://dnnazureaccelerator.codeplex.com/ for more information.
Click the Next button to begin the process.
